Dialogue: 10,0:00:02.94,0:00:06.06,Default,Saint,0,0,0,,{\i1}We wanted nothing more\Nthan to have someone by our side.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:07.65,0:00:10.36,Default,Saint,0,0,0,,{\i1}We had power.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:11.56,0:00:14.74,Default,Saint,0,0,0,,{\i1}We ceased to be alone.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:15.15,0:00:17.97,Default,Saint,0,0,0,,{\i1}But at the end of that humble happiness...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:32.36,0:00:36.01,Default,Saint,0,0,0,,{\i1}...lay nought but death and despair.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:46.25,0:00:49.52,Default,Saint,0,0,0,,{\i1}Subsequently, we were reborn.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:56.49,0:00:58.57,Default,Saint,0,0,0,,{\i1}We soon realized...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:58.57,0:01:02.70,Default,Saint,0,0,0,,{\i1}that we were fated to pass down our memories,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:02.70,0:01:05.34,Default,Saint,0,0,0,,{\i1}our emotions, to another "us".
Dialogue: 10,0:01:05.34,0:01:08.91,Default,Saint,0,0,0,,{\i1}We were to watch over this world till its final days.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:12.91,0:01:18.47,Default,Saint,0,0,0,,{\i1}There was no doubt that love, beauty,\Nand virtue existed within this world,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:18.47,0:01:24.42,Default,Saint,0,0,0,,{\i1}but even more so did hatred, ugliness, and folly.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:24.42,0:01:27.59,Default,Saint,0,0,0,,{\i1}Each time we were born into this world,\Nits grip upon us tightened.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:27.59,0:01:33.77,Default,Saint,0,0,0,,{\i1}And little by little,\Nthat impurity gnawed away at our hearts.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:33.77,0:01:34.86,Default,Saint,0,0,0,,Then,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:35.40,0:01:38.01,Default,Saint,0,0,0,,a great many years later,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:38.01,0:01:43.37,Default,Saint,0,0,0,,our modest desire had twisted into disgust\Nand despair at mankind's nature.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:43.37,0:01:45.15,Default,Saint,0,0,0,,Does humanity...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:45.15,0:01:46.76,Default,Saint,0,0,0,,Does life...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:47.65,0:01:52.38,Default,Saint,0,0,0,,...truly deserve to be a part of the future?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:59.05,0:02:01.14,Default,Aka,0,0,0,,Wh-What was that?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:03.78,0:02:05.20,Default,Aka,0,0,0,,Shimako...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:05.20,0:02:06.70,Default,Aka,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:06.70,0:02:07.90,Default,Aka,0,0,0,,I'm all right.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:09.59,0:02:11.51,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,According to Sakuya's report,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:11.51,0:02:15.11,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,Kotori's secret base should\Nbe around here somewhere...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:17.48,0:02:19.11,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,I just heard a voice.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:19.71,0:02:20.33,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:20.33,0:02:21.76,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,K-Konohana-san?!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:21.76,0:02:23.62,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,Wh-What are you doing here?!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:26.87,0:02:29.13,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,You're gravely wounded!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:29.67,0:02:32.25,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,Hold on! I'll get you to a hospital right away!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:32.25,0:02:33.50,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Over here?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:33.50,0:02:34.51,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:34.51,0:02:36.76,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,There was some strange feedback in the barrier.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:38.88,0:02:40.29,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,Kotarou!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:40.29,0:02:41.26,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,Kotori!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:41.26,0:02:42.51,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:16.98,0:04:19.49,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,I'd heard about it from Sakuya,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:19.49,0:04:21.89,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,but to think there really was\Na place like this in the forest...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:21.89,0:04:24.16,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,Anyway, hurry up and come this way.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:24.16,0:04:25.57,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:27.41,0:04:29.06,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:29.06,0:04:32.21,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,I'm revitalizing Class Rep's life force.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:32.21,0:04:35.33,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,It's kind of like breathing life into daemons.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:36.99,0:04:39.84,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,So you really are a summoner?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:39.84,0:04:41.41,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:41.41,0:04:42.97,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,A druid, specifically...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:45.98,0:04:49.35,Default,Saku,0,0,0,,It would appear a fierce battle took place here.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:49.69,0:04:51.10,Default,Saku,0,0,0,,One combatant used flames.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:51.61,0:04:52.98,Default,Saku,0,0,0,,As for the other...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:53.43,0:04:54.60,Default,Saku,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:54.60,0:04:56.69,Default,Saku,0,0,0,,Could you take a deep breath for me?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:56.69,0:04:57.57,Default,Giru,0,0,0,,Sure thing!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:03.09,0:05:05.24,Default,Saku,0,0,0,,As I suspected, it is indeed poison.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:05.24,0:05:08.24,Default,Saku,0,0,0,,This entire area has been\Ncompletely and utterly contaminated.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:08.24,0:05:11.99,Default,Giru,0,0,0,,Don't use me like a canary in a coal mine!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:17.29,0:05:18.29,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Lucia!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:17.29,0:05:18.29,Default - Alt,Chi,0,0,0,,Konohana-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:18.29,0:05:19.70,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,The bleeding...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:19.70,0:05:22.30,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,The bleeding won't stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:22.79,0:05:25.93,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,Wouldn't her condition improve if you used this?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:25.93,0:05:27.69,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,Just saying.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:27.69,0:05:30.61,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Kagari, this is no time for playing around—
Dialogue: 10,0:05:30.61,0:05:31.68,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:34.64,0:05:35.75,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:36.25,0:05:38.69,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,I'll use it, Kagari.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:47.25,0:05:50.04,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,She still needs to get some rest,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:50.04,0:05:51.47,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,but she should be okay now.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:51.47,0:05:52.62,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Really?!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:53.67,0:05:55.71,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,Th-Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:57.69,0:05:58.81,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,How about that?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:58.81,0:06:00.44,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,All thanks to yours truly!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:00.44,0:06:02.88,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,I put the "K" in "Key", 'kay?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:02.88,0:06:04.24,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Kagari!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:04.24,0:06:05.09,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:05.09,0:06:06.34,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,Oh wow!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:06.34,0:06:08.38,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Thank you, Kagari.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:08.38,0:06:12.20,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for saving Lucia.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:16.60,0:06:19.43,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,You're being awfully touchy-feely, Kotarou.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:19.43,0:06:20.15,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:20.15,0:06:21.06,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:21.06,0:06:22.39,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Not the face!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:21.59,0:06:23.36,Default - Alt,Chi,0,0,0,,What are they doing?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:25.13,0:06:26.28,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:26.28,0:06:27.74,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,That girl is the Key?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:28.09,0:06:29.11,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,Class Rep.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:29.11,0:06:30.06,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Lucia...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:30.06,0:06:31.12,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,Konohana-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:31.12,0:06:35.11,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,I never thought I'd be able\Nto see her with my own two eyes.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:35.11,0:06:37.97,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,Rumors need to be taken with a pinch of salt, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:37.97,0:06:39.99,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,Is it okay for you to be talking?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:39.99,0:06:40.91,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:40.91,0:06:43.44,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,I can't believe how much the pain has subsided.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:43.44,0:06:45.77,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,Is this also the power of the Key?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:45.77,0:06:47.98,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,I'd like to show my gratitude.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:47.98,0:06:49.51,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,Thank you, Kotarou.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:51.05,0:06:52.41,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,And you too, Kanbe-sa—
Dialogue: 10,0:06:53.56,0:06:55.56,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,Thank you, Kotori.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:55.56,0:06:56.43,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,Chihaya.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:57.95,0:07:00.44,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,You're welcome, Lucy!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:00.44,0:07:02.34,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,L-Lucy?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:02.34,0:07:05.19,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,You went way over the top, Lucia!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:05.19,0:07:08.13,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,By the way, who are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:08.13,0:07:09.35,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,You're asking that {\i1}now{\i0}?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:09.35,0:07:11.40,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Um, how to put it...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:11.40,0:07:16.78,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,From your perspective,\NI suppose I would be considered the enemy.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:16.78,0:07:17.65,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,The enemy?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:17.65,0:07:18.78,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:18.78,0:07:19.68,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,I'm with Guardi—
Dialogue: 10,0:07:19.68,0:07:20.59,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,She's a friend!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:20.59,0:07:21.33,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:21.33,0:07:22.36,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:22.36,0:07:25.36,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,She's a fellow member of the\Noccult club, and a friend of ours!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:25.36,0:07:27.34,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,Yeah, we're friends!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:27.34,0:07:28.29,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:30.25,0:07:32.20,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:33.94,0:07:37.10,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,That's really all that mattered.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:37.51,0:07:38.41,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,Lucy?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:38.41,0:07:40.42,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Lucia?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:40.42,0:07:42.56,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,Are you hungry or something?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:43.19,0:07:44.70,Default,Saku,0,0,0,,I have returned.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:45.71,0:07:47.94,Default,Saku,0,0,0,,It seems she's through the worst of it.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:47.94,0:07:48.62,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:48.62,0:07:50.62,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,As long as she rests for a few days,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:50.62,0:07:52.83,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,I believe she'll recover her former mobility.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:52.83,0:07:53.83,Default,Saku,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:53.83,0:07:55.79,Default,Saku,0,0,0,,In that case, I shall reinforce the barrier
Dialogue: 10,0:07:55.79,0:07:57.56,Default,Saku,0,0,0,,and extend my scouting range.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:57.56,0:07:58.39,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Please do.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:58.39,0:08:01.64,Default,Saku,0,0,0,,I will also step up your training.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:01.64,0:08:03.77,Default,Saku,0,0,0,,As a form of personal stress relief.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:03.77,0:08:04.63,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:11.13,0:08:12.54,Default,Aka,0,0,0,,Chihaya...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:13.10,0:08:16.64,Default,Aka,0,0,0,,I hope she was able to meet up\Nwith everyone successfully...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:20.35,0:08:24.09,Default,Kashi,0,0,0,,Shuuichiro, who do I look like to you?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:24.09,0:08:27.05,Default,Kashi,0,0,0,,Am I still myself?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:27.05,0:08:28.93,Default,Shu,0,0,0,,You are Sakura.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:28.93,0:08:30.82,Default,Shu,0,0,0,,You're still my Sakura.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:33.21,0:08:35.44,Default,Aka,0,0,0,,That was Grandmother's...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:35.44,0:08:37.87,Default,Aka,0,0,0,,Don't tell me this is the saint's...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:42.87,0:08:44.13,Default,Aka,0,0,0,,It's me.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:44.13,0:08:45.20,Default,Aka,0,0,0,,Tsukuno?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:45.20,0:08:46.43,Default,Aka,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:47.71,0:08:49.38,Default,Aka,0,0,0,,Grandmother collapsed?!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:52.70,0:08:53.48,Default,Aka,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:53.48,0:08:54.93,Default,Aka,0,0,0,,I'll be right there.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:58.68,0:09:00.14,Default,Tou,0,0,0,,Shizuru-chan.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:00.14,0:09:01.35,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Touka?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:01.35,0:09:03.93,Default,Tou,0,0,0,,I haven't seen Lucia-chan since last night.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:03.93,0:09:05.59,Default,Tou,0,0,0,,Happen to know where she might be?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:06.20,0:09:07.90,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,N-No.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:08.99,0:09:10.15,Default,Tou,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:12.11,0:09:13.86,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,I-Is that safe?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:13.86,0:09:17.18,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Don't living creatures melt when they touch that?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:17.18,0:09:18.87,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,Inorganic objects are fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:19.75,0:09:20.69,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:21.46,0:09:22.62,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,Just my imagination.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:25.93,0:09:27.75,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,Lucy's condition has stabilized,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:27.75,0:09:30.50,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,so we have to bolster our forces while we still can.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:31.22,0:09:33.37,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Is this how daemons are made?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:33.37,0:09:34.09,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:34.09,0:09:36.92,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,By giving them a body and forming a contract,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:36.92,0:09:38.51,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,I can bring them to life and use them.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:38.83,0:09:43.19,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,Honestly, though, using an animal's\Ncorpse would be most effective.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:43.19,0:09:44.45,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,A-A corpse?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:45.27,0:09:46.52,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,Done.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:46.52,0:09:48.65,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,Now just a little of this...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:52.48,0:09:54.50,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Oh, it actually moved!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:54.50,0:09:55.75,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:55.75,0:09:56.65,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:57.04,0:09:59.78,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,Did I mess up somehow?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:11.96,0:10:15.32,Default,Mido,0,0,0,,Yo, Greenhouse Princess.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:15.32,0:10:18.46,Default,Mido,0,0,0,,Your little friends are playing a fun game\Nof hide and seek in the forest.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:19.18,0:10:21.23,Default,Mido,0,0,0,,What, they leave you out in the cold?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:21.23,0:10:23.34,Default,Aka,0,0,0,,It sounds like you've done your homework.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:23.34,0:10:26.89,Default,Mido,0,0,0,,On the battlefield,\Nignorant shits always bite the dust first.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:26.89,0:10:30.37,Default,Mido,0,0,0,,I ain't like those peace-loving\Ndumbasses in this country.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:31.48,0:10:34.61,Default,Aka,0,0,0,,You're Fogo's master, if I'm not mistaken?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:36.05,0:10:39.15,Default,Mido,0,0,0,,The hell you planning to do\Nwith the Key by bringing the Apex
Dialogue: 10,0:10:39.15,0:10:42.62,Default,Mido,0,0,0,,and that stray superhuman together in the forest?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:43.05,0:10:44.54,Default,Aka,0,0,0,,What are you after?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:44.54,0:10:46.80,Default,Mido,0,0,0,,They're {\i1}my{\i0} prey!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:46.80,0:10:48.54,Default,Mido,0,0,0,,If you're gonna fuck around from the sidelines,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:48.54,0:10:50.07,Default,Mido,0,0,0,,I don't give a shit if you're Gaia.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:50.07,0:10:50.99,Default,Mido,0,0,0,,I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:50.99,0:10:52.41,Default,Mido,0,0,0,,That's all.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:52.41,0:10:53.25,Default,Mido,0,0,0,,Keep that in mind!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:55.25,0:10:56.97,Default,Aka,0,0,0,,Poison, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:56.97,0:10:58.92,Default,Aka,0,0,0,,A powerful one at that.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:58.92,0:11:01.30,Default,Mido,0,0,0,,What about it?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:01.30,0:11:05.81,Default,Aka,0,0,0,,What if I said I'd grant you a new power?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:05.81,0:11:07.01,Default,Mido,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:12.83,0:11:14.65,Default,Mido,0,0,0,,This is the legendary...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:14.65,0:11:15.28,Default,Aka,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:15.28,0:11:16.96,Default,Aka,0,0,0,,Save for the Apex,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:16.96,0:11:19.50,Default,Aka,0,0,0,,it's undoubtedly Gaia's ultimate weapon:
Dialogue: 10,0:11:19.50,0:11:20.54,Default,Aka,0,0,0,,the Earth Dragon.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:20.54,0:11:24.07,Default,Aka,0,0,0,,If you accept my condition, I'll give this to you.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:24.07,0:11:29.83,Default,Aka,0,0,0,,However, this daemon will consume\Nyour life force faster than any other.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:29.83,0:11:31.73,Default,Mido,0,0,0,,Don't underestimate me!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:31.73,0:11:34.54,Default,Mido,0,0,0,,Not just anyone could use Fogo, either.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:35.09,0:11:38.01,Default,Mido,0,0,0,,So, what's the condition?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:38.01,0:11:40.06,Default,Aka,0,0,0,,That you don't kill the Key.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:40.06,0:11:43.77,Default,Aka,0,0,0,,Even if Guardian attacks, you must protect it.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:43.77,0:11:45.55,Default,Mido,0,0,0,,Damn, what a pain.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:45.55,0:11:46.36,Default,Aka,0,0,0,,Got it?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:46.36,0:11:47.89,Default,Aka,0,0,0,,If anything happens to the Key,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:47.89,0:11:50.60,Default,Aka,0,0,0,,this damned world you detest\Noh so much will continue on.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:52.96,0:11:54.17,Default,Mido,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:54.17,0:11:55.69,Default,Mido,0,0,0,,But aside from the Key,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:55.69,0:11:58.51,Default,Mido,0,0,0,,everything is my prey,\Nincluding your happy little friends.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:58.51,0:11:59.79,Default,Mido,0,0,0,,You okay with that?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:59.79,0:12:01.33,Default,Aka,0,0,0,,Do as you please.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:01.33,0:12:05.49,Default,Aka,0,0,0,,Life is not deserving of a place in the future.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:06.59,0:12:08.81,Default,Mido,0,0,0,,I like you, Princess.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:08.81,0:12:12.01,Default,Mido,0,0,0,,I'll crush everything in my path!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:26.63,0:12:31.14,Default,Pani,0,0,0,,Gil-chan tried to attack Kotarou-san\Nduring his training and got crushed!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:31.14,0:12:32.27,Default,Saku,0,0,0,,Good grief.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:34.15,0:12:37.14,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,The daemons do seem to be acting funny.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:37.14,0:12:39.22,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,It only started recently.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:39.22,0:12:41.57,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,Do you have any idea why?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:41.57,0:12:43.30,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,According to Sakuya-san,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:43.30,0:12:46.58,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,the soil in this area has been\Ncontaminated with poison.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:46.58,0:12:50.12,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,I think the power spot has\Nbeen acting up because of it.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:50.12,0:12:52.11,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,Poison?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:52.11,0:12:54.42,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,That most likely means it's my fault.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:54.42,0:12:56.05,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:56.05,0:12:56.87,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:56.87,0:12:58.83,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,Oh, you don't look well.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:58.83,0:13:02.02,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,Very well. I shall share\Nmy cherished feecof with thee.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:02.02,0:13:03.75,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,Huh? N-No, I...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:03.75,0:13:04.43,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,Gulp it.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:04.43,0:13:06.01,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,Come on, gulp it!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:06.01,0:13:08.19,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,Hey, my body still isn't—
Dialogue: 10,0:13:11.34,0:13:13.43,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,Lucia! Are you all right?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:13.43,0:13:15.58,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,Ow...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:16.54,0:13:18.28,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,What a waste.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:18.28,0:13:19.44,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,Lick, lick!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:19.44,0:13:22.13,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,D-Don't lick my face!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:22.13,0:13:23.54,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,Hey! Stop it!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:23.54,0:13:24.45,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,{\an8}It tickles!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:23.54,0:13:24.45,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:25.06,0:13:26.66,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,H-Hey, let me down!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:26.66,0:13:30.53,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,But Lucia, you haven't recovered\Nyour strength yet, have you?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:30.53,0:13:32.42,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,Isn't she heavy, Chi-chan?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:32.42,0:13:34.23,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,Th-That's rude, Kotori!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:34.23,0:13:35.58,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:35.58,0:13:39.29,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,I'm strong due to the influence\Nof the daemon I've contracted with.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:39.29,0:13:41.30,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,The daemon you've contracted with?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:43.09,0:13:45.97,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,Oh, so that's how it is.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:48.47,0:13:50.00,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,This is total bliss!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:50.00,0:13:50.80,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:50.80,0:13:52.47,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,You aren't taking off your gloves?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:54.00,0:13:54.81,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:55.49,0:13:56.91,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:56.91,0:13:59.08,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,I started to mention this earlier,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:59.08,0:14:02.98,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,but I'm the source of the poison\Nthat polluted this forest.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:02.98,0:14:04.49,Default,Both,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:09.00,0:14:10.25,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:10.25,0:14:11.99,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,That was insensitive of me.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:12.30,0:14:14.58,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,You're saying even flowers are dirty?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:15.01,0:14:16.83,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,It's all water under the bridge now.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:17.25,0:14:18.50,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:18.50,0:14:20.52,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,No, I won't accept that!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:20.52,0:14:21.84,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,Ch-Chi-chan?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:21.84,0:14:23.90,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,Why do you have to suffer like that?!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:23.90,0:14:28.00,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,I'm sure that deep down, you actually\Ndo want to touch flowers and animals!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:28.00,0:14:31.32,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,Save the world from destruction,\Nno matter the cost.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:31.32,0:14:33.37,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,That is Guardian's mission.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:33.37,0:14:34.33,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:34.33,0:14:35.85,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,It feels so strange.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:36.37,0:14:39.31,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,A member of Gaia,\Nwho is trying to destroy humanity,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:39.31,0:14:41.26,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,is worried about my well-being.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:41.26,0:14:43.90,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,That's because I'm your friend!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:43.90,0:14:44.86,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,Mhm!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:45.86,0:14:47.24,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:47.69,0:14:49.36,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,It doesn't make sense.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:51.13,0:14:52.87,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,H-Hey, you're totally exposed!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:52.87,0:14:58.65,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,Gaia and Guardian say they're working\Ntoward the same goal of saving the world,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:58.65,0:15:02.25,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,but I can't imagine that's true\Nbased on what I've just heard.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:02.25,0:15:03.90,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:03.90,0:15:06.52,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,That may not have been\Nenough of an explanation.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:08.61,0:15:09.40,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:09.40,0:15:11.89,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Man, that Sakuya really\Ndoesn't know how to go easy, huh.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:12.34,0:15:14.21,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Better wash off the sweat right away...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:15.89,0:15:16.64,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:21.06,0:15:23.19,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,K-Kotarou, you...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:23.19,0:15:24.99,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,What are you thinking?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:24.99,0:15:26.44,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,No debauchery! Let's keep it PG!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:26.44,0:15:28.05,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,I-I'm not doing it on purpose!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:28.05,0:15:30.41,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,I always come here to wash up after training—
Dialogue: 10,0:15:47.65,0:15:48.59,Default,Saku,0,0,0,,Here you are.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:54.21,0:15:56.96,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,Nothing beats a canned feecof right after a bath.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:57.55,0:16:00.00,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Yeah, I've been wondering about that, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:00.00,0:16:04.44,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Why are Gaia and Guardian fighting\Nwhen they have the same goal?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:08.60,0:16:12.65,Default,Saku,0,0,0,,Although our goals are similar,\Nthe essence is quite different.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:13.17,0:16:15.37,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Hey, you're coughing up blood.\NDon't push yourself!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:15.37,0:16:20.98,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,Gaia's goal is to eradicate humanity\Nand regenerate this world.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:20.98,0:16:21.70,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:21.70,0:16:26.62,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,On the other hand, Guardian's mission is\Nto preserve the world that mankind has built.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:26.62,0:16:27.32,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:27.32,0:16:31.51,Default,Saku,0,0,0,,It is correct that both wish\Nto save the world in a broad sense.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:31.51,0:16:33.16,Default,Saku,0,0,0,,And druids...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:33.16,0:16:36.30,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,...exist to protect the Key\Nuntil it hands down its judgment.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:36.30,0:16:39.60,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,As for what sort of Salvation\Nthe Key will bring about,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:39.60,0:16:42.10,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,we're honestly not too worried about it.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:42.10,0:16:45.01,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,They're all so extreme.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:46.12,0:16:47.11,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,Yummy.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:47.59,0:16:49.49,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,This question might be a little late as well...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:48.71,0:16:50.72,Default,Giru,0,0,0,,{\an8}Whoa! What is this?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:49.96,0:16:53.86,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,What are Gaia and Guardian\Ngoing to do with the Key, anyway?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:50.72,0:16:51.75,Default,Giru,0,0,0,,{\an8}Awesome!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:51.75,0:16:53.36,Default,Pani,0,0,0,,{\an8}It's so pretty!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:57.37,0:16:59.70,Default,Saku,0,0,0,,To be blunt, we'll shelter her.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:59.70,0:17:00.48,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Shelter?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:00.48,0:17:01.39,Default,Saku,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:01.39,0:17:04.82,Default,Saku,0,0,0,,We know scant in regard\Nto the Salvation she will bring,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:04.82,0:17:07.68,Default,Saku,0,0,0,,and thus we must keep\Nher secure until then to learn.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:07.68,0:17:09.10,Default,Saku,0,0,0,,That goes for Gaia.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:09.10,0:17:10.39,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,For Gaia?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:10.39,0:17:12.76,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Then, what will Guardian do?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:13.33,0:17:14.48,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,We'll erase it.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:14.48,0:17:15.01,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:15.32,0:17:19.41,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,As long as there is no guarantee\Nthis Salvation will benefit humanity,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:19.41,0:17:22.14,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,we will erase the Key to maintain the status quo.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:22.14,0:17:24.39,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,That's Guardian's train of thought.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:24.39,0:17:27.02,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,You'll kill Kagari?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:32.01,0:17:33.84,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,How terrible.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:33.84,0:17:36.93,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,Who would have thought there\Nwas such a reason to fight over me?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:37.45,0:17:40.38,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,I am indeed a temptress!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:40.38,0:17:41.24,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:41.24,0:17:43.04,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,It isn't easy being popular, is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:46.74,0:17:48.00,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,Lucy?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:49.63,0:17:53.42,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,Oh, I have no intention\Nof harming Kagari anymore.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:54.24,0:17:58.50,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,I couldn't kill someone who's saved my life,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:58.50,0:18:02.56,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,and who can talk to me, even for humanity's sake.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:03.98,0:18:05.38,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:05.38,0:18:06.36,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,At the very least,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:06.36,0:18:09.39,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,this means we won't end up\Nfighting you anymore, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:09.39,0:18:10.31,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,Mhm!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:11.57,0:18:12.41,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,That's great!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:12.41,0:18:14.08,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,We're all like bees in a pod!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:14.08,0:18:15.33,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,You mean peas...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:15.33,0:18:17.16,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,I don't get it.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:17.16,0:18:19.81,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,If you are able to resolve your\Ndifferences with conversation,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:19.81,0:18:22.45,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,why do the majority of humans not do so?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:23.87,0:18:24.98,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:24.98,0:18:27.33,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,I studied many things.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:29.31,0:18:31.43,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,Humans have continued to chip away
Dialogue: 10,0:18:31.43,0:18:33.95,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,at the planet's lifespan\Nthrough destruction and strife.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:33.95,0:18:37.59,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,Wasting energy like that\Nis nothing short of pointless.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:37.93,0:18:39.92,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,Foolish humans should
Dialogue: 10,0:18:39.92,0:18:43.60,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,at least give a little more thought\Nto how they use energy.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:48.85,0:18:53.00,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,Even I can't eat any more...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:59.86,0:19:02.08,Default,Aka,0,0,0,,{\i1}Accelerating environmental destruction.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:02.08,0:19:03.86,Default,Aka,0,0,0,,{\i1}Resources on the verge of exhaustion.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:03.86,0:19:07.26,Default,Aka,0,0,0,,{\i1}And yet a segment of humanity\Ncontinues to indulge in their pleasures
Dialogue: 10,0:19:07.26,0:19:09.83,Default,Aka,0,0,0,,{\i1}without any sense of impending danger.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:10.06,0:19:12.25,Default,Aka,0,0,0,,Just get rid of the humans.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:12.31,0:19:15.38,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Foolish humans, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:28.57,0:19:29.27,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Kagari.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:29.85,0:19:31.07,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,Oh, Kotarou?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:31.07,0:19:32.02,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,Is this a booty call?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:32.02,0:19:33.56,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,No, it's not!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:33.56,0:19:36.00,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,I just remembered someone\Nwho said something similar
Dialogue: 10,0:19:36.00,0:19:37.61,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,to what you did.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:37.61,0:19:38.48,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Say...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:38.48,0:19:41.92,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Are humans really useless\Nas far as the Earth is concerned?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:41.92,0:19:43.29,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,Let me see.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:43.29,0:19:46.84,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,It is true that humans are foolish compared to me.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:46.84,0:19:49.17,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,I have learned that well by watching you.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:49.17,0:19:50.04,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:50.04,0:19:53.61,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,But humans do have their decent points.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:53.61,0:19:56.29,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,I also learned that well by watching you.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:57.55,0:20:00.55,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,So, by putting those aspects to good use—
Dialogue: 10,0:20:02.19,0:20:03.22,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Kagari?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:05.77,0:20:08.43,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,Good... memories...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:08.43,0:20:10.01,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Good memories?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:10.01,0:20:10.68,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,What's that supposed—
Dialogue: 10,0:20:12.14,0:20:13.12,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Kagari?!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:13.12,0:20:14.07,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,What are you...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:14.07,0:20:14.90,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:14.90,0:20:17.52,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,Good... memor—
Dialogue: 10,0:20:17.89,0:20:18.70,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Kagari!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:18.70,0:20:19.78,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Hey, Kagari!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:23.10,0:20:24.66,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,So it {\i1}was{\i0} a booty call.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:27.54,0:20:28.91,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:50.24,0:20:51.98,Default,Mido,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep ya!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:55.90,0:20:57.08,Default,Mido,0,0,0,,Let's move.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:59.69,0:21:03.18,Default,Aka,0,0,0,,Playtime is over, humans.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:05.71,0:21:06.92,Default,Aka,0,0,0,,No,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:06.92,0:21:09.70,Default,Aka,0,0,0,,I won't let you end it yet.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:11.20,0:21:12.80,Default,Ima,0,0,0,,So rough!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:12.80,0:21:14.07,Default,Ima,0,0,0,,Finding so much evidence
Dialogue: 10,0:21:14.07,0:21:17.07,Default,Ima,0,0,0,,while patrolling the Harvest\NFesta was seriously rough!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:17.07,0:21:18.22,Default,Ex,0,0,0,,Imamiya-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:18.22,0:21:21.20,Default,Ex,0,0,0,,We've lost contact with Charlie,\Nwho was scouting the forest!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:21.20,0:21:22.13,Default,Ima,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:22.13,0:21:24.23,Default,Ima,0,0,0,,That's when you send Bravo to check on them—
Dialogue: 10,0:21:24.23,0:21:26.34,Default,Ex,0,0,0,,We cannot get in touch with Bravo, either!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:26.83,0:21:28.35,Default,Ima,0,0,0,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:28.35,0:21:29.51,Default,Esa,0,0,0,,{\an8}A short while ago,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:29.51,0:21:32.85,Default,Esa,0,0,0,,{\an8}we lost contact with both the Bravo\Nand Charlie scouting parties.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:35.23,0:21:39.36,Default,Esa,0,0,0,,We must assume that a considerably\Npowerful daemon has been sent in.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:39.36,0:21:41.48,Default,Esa,0,0,0,,Doing that at this juncture must mean...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:42.03,0:21:44.49,Default,Gen,0,0,0,,The Key is involved?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:44.49,0:21:46.06,Default,Esa,0,0,0,,It is very likely.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:46.06,0:21:49.84,Default,Esa,0,0,0,,Accordingly, I have decided to send in\Ncombat troops immediately.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:49.84,0:21:52.07,Default,Esa,0,0,0,,We lost contact with the scouting party...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:52.71,0:21:53.50,Default,Esa,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:53.50,0:21:54.75,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:16.80,0:22:19.02,Default,Ka,0,0,0,,{\i1}Do you hear it?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:19.77,0:22:22.71,Default,Ka,0,0,0,,{\i1}If so, join them in unison...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:22.71,0:22:25.11,Default,Ka,0,0,0,,{\i1}The song of destruction...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:25.72,0:22:27.63,Default,Ka,0,0,0,,{\i1}which will bring salvation to the world!
Comment: 0,0:22:27.63,0:22:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,OP
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.23,0:03:04.56,OP-E,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2\3c&HF6F5D2&}Little by little, the ripples drew apart from one another
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.23,0:03:04.56,OP-R,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2\3c&HF6F5D2&}sukoshizutsu hamon wa hanarete itta
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.56,0:03:09.32,OP-E,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2\3c&HF6F5D2&}And before we knew it, they no longer overlapped
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.56,0:03:09.32,OP-R,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2\3c&HF6F5D2&}itsu shika hitotsu mo kasanaranaku natta
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.32,0:03:17.66,OP-E,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2\3c&HF6F5D2&}But it's okay as long as you're here with me
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.32,0:03:17.66,OP-R,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2\3c&HF6F5D2&}sore demo ii kimi to itara
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.16,0:03:25.54,OP-E,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2\3c&HF6F5D2&}When did I start feeling this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.16,0:03:25.54,OP-R,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2\3c&HF6F5D2&}konna kimochi itsu kara idaita
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.54,0:03:35.51,OP-E,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2\3c&HF6F5D2&}This is the love story of a certain boy
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.54,0:03:35.51,OP-R,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2\3c&HF6F5D2&}tada hitori no shounen no koimonogatari da
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.64,0:03:41.73,OP-E,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2\3c&HF6F5D2&}To protect you till the end of time
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.64,0:03:41.73,OP-R,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2\3c&HF6F5D2&}eien ni kimi wo mamotte miseru
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.73,0:03:47.02,OP-E,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2\3c&HF6F5D2&}I'll etch this upon my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.73,0:03:47.02,OP-R,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2\3c&HF6F5D2&}kono mune ni kizamikomu
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.02,0:03:52.36,OP-E,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2\3c&HF6F5D2&}When did it start being just the two of us, again?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.02,0:03:52.36,OP-R,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2\3c&HF6F5D2&}itsu kara futarikiri ni natta n da kke
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.36,0:03:54.99,OP-E,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2\3c&HF6F5D2&}But it's okay
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.36,0:03:54.99,OP-R,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2\3c&HF6F5D2&}mou ii ka
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.99,0:04:00.29,OP-E,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2\3c&HF6F5D2&}Just smile
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.99,0:04:00.29,OP-R,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2\3c&HF6F5D2&}sonna koto waratte yo
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.29,0:04:06.29,OP-E,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2\3c&HF6F5D2&}On the eve of this world's end
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.29,0:04:06.29,OP-R,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2\3c&HF6F5D2&}owaru sono hi ni wa
Comment: 0,0:22:29.63,0:22:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,ED
Dialogue: 6,0:22:31.93,0:22:39.48,ED2-R,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(150,150)\blur1}natsukashisa mo kieta yume
Dialogue: 5,0:22:31.93,0:22:39.48,ED2-E,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(150,150)\blur1}Losing myself in a dream where even nostalgia lost form
Dialogue: 6,0:22:39.48,0:22:47.37,ED2-R,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(150,150)\blur1}mayoi kono te ga samishiku kaze wo nadeta
Dialogue: 5,0:22:39.48,0:22:47.37,ED2-E,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(150,150)\blur1}Lonely, I reached out with my hands to feel the wind's gentle caress
Dialogue: 6,0:22:47.37,0:22:54.41,ED2-R,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(150,150)\blur1}kotoba wo shiranai mama naraba
Dialogue: 5,0:22:47.37,0:22:54.41,ED2-E,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(150,150)\blur1}The names of those emotions still eluded me
Dialogue: 6,0:22:54.41,0:22:59.21,ED2-R,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(150,150)\blur1}kono hitomi wo tojiru koto mo
Dialogue: 5,0:22:54.41,0:22:59.21,ED2-E,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(150,150)\blur1}Even closing my eyes for eternity
Dialogue: 6,0:22:59.21,0:23:03.88,ED2-R,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(150,150)\blur1}kantan datta no ni
Dialogue: 5,0:22:59.21,0:23:03.88,ED2-E,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(150,150)\blur1}Should have been simple
Dialogue: 6,0:23:03.88,0:23:10.68,ED2-R,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(150,150)\blur1}hajimete fureta nukumori
Dialogue: 5,0:23:03.88,0:23:10.68,ED2-E,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(150,150)\blur1}But I felt warmth for the first time
Dialogue: 6,0:23:10.68,0:23:16.14,ED2-R,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(150,150)\blur1}chiisaku mebuku kodou ni
Dialogue: 5,0:23:10.68,0:23:16.14,ED2-E,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(150,150)\blur1}A tiny soul began to bud within my heart
Dialogue: 6,0:23:16.14,0:23:21.48,ED2-R,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(150,150)\blur1}tomadoi wo oboeta
Dialogue: 5,0:23:16.14,0:23:21.48,ED2-E,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(150,150)\blur1}And I learned of bewilderment
Dialogue: 6,0:23:24.15,0:23:31.87,ED2-R,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(150,150)\blur1}anata no koe sagashite mugen no michi wo yuku
Dialogue: 5,0:23:24.15,0:23:31.87,ED2-E,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(150,150)\blur1}Walking on the path of eternity, searching for your voice
Dialogue: 6,0:23:31.87,0:23:39.58,ED2-R,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(150,150)\blur1}hoshi no hajimari wo shiru tada sore dake
Dialogue: 5,0:23:31.87,0:23:39.58,ED2-E,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(150,150)\blur1}I'm led to the time when stars are born, nothing more
Dialogue: 6,0:23:39.58,0:23:47.47,ED2-R,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(150,150)\blur1}kuchi ni nokoru nigami mo hiroku mada ki ni naru
Dialogue: 5,0:23:39.58,0:23:47.47,ED2-E,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(150,150)\blur1}This bitterness that lingers inside my mouth tempts my curiosity
Dialogue: 6,0:23:47.47,0:23:56.81,ED2-R,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(150,150)\blur1}itsuka deau anata he saigo ni hohoemi wo
Dialogue: 5,0:23:47.47,0:23:56.81,ED2-E,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(150,150)\blur1}So I'll offer you one last smile before we meet again
